    Create 19 Sector Input-Output Table.

    create_19_sector.Rd

    Creates a 19 Sector Input-Output Table by aggregating the 114 Sector Input-Output Table (see: create_114_sector())

    Usage

    create_19_sector(path = NULL)

    Value

    tibble of the industry-industry flows between 19 ANZSIC Sectors for Australia.

    Examples

    create_19_sector()
